<F P=103> LD2001130294 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UKRINFORM </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By UKRINFORM correspondents Viktor Demydenko and Oleksiy </F>
Petrunya] 
  [Text] Kiev, 20 Jan--The Kazakh president's plane has just 
landed at Boryspil international airport, where the state flags 
of Ukraine and the Republic of Kazakhstan were hoisted. 
  At the aircraft's ramp, Nursultan Nazarbayev was met by 
Acting Ukrainian Prime Minister Yukhym Zvyahilskyy, Foreign 
