  [Text] Moscow January 20 TASS -- Russia will ship to North 
Korea several decommissioned submarines intended for scrap, 
Russian Foreign Ministry spokesman Grigoriy Karasin told a 
briefing on Thursday. 
  These are not military equipment deliveries, but a 
commercial 
