<F P=102>  LD2201190094 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 
1700 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2201190094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vesti" newscast] </F>
  [Text] A large-scale military exercise by the Ukrainian 
Armed Forces is planned in the Crimea for the end of January. 
In connection with this, representatives of a number of Crimean 
organizations are pointing out that these maneuvers are being 
carried out just before the second round of presidential 
elections in the Crimea, scheduled for 30 January. Meanwhile, 
the Ukrainian Defense Ministry press service has reported that 
the exercises set for January are planned and represent training 
for territorial defense. 

</TEXT>

