<H3> <TI>   Frontline Fighting Resumes in Nagorno-Karabakh </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC2201105894 Yerevan SNARK in English 0919 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC2201105894 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, January 22 (SNARK)--Today the 
Azerbaijani troops have resumed their attacks after a days 
respite towards the Armenian positions of Madaghis and Akop 
Kamari [names as received] villages. By 10 o'clock violent 
fights went on there. 
  The Karabakh Defence Army Headquarters told SNARK the 
Karabakh forces reject the enemy's attacks. 
  The positional fights take place at the other parts of the 
front. 

</TEXT>

