Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS parliamentary corespondent Ivan Novikov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow January 21 TASS -- The Russian State Duma 
turned down on Friday a proposal to adopt an official statement 
on the new composition of the government, but agreed to discuss 
the situation in former Yugoslavia and consider the resumption 
