<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   Federov May Join `Union of 12 December' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2301093694 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0800 GMT 
23 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2301093694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Boris Fedorov has said that he will join a State 
Duma faction of liberal and reformist character called the 
"Union of December 12." Radio Liberty reports that he 
understood that he might remain in the shadow of Gaydar without 
the support of people who hold the same views. Irina Khakamada, 
the leader of this union, believes that Fedorov is a man who has 
a clear program. 

</TEXT>

